name: [LoRa] Clearlight 清光 Concept (With multires noise version)
description:
※A LoRa model trained by a friend with multires noise & block weights.

This is a LoRa model that trained by 200+ img generated with NijiV5,and it's the multires noise version.

This model can achieve more detailed cold light & shadow segmentation effects and depict the different parts of scenery under light in the winter.

weight 1.0 maybe generates better img.
